result.name: Shaz Confections

reviews.text: Nice crepe cake, I tried matcha and was better than Lady X. Good coffee too. Should try if you're in the neighborhood.
Delicious crepe cakes with variety choices of flavor. Enjoyable nice breakfast in a cosy shop. Friendly staffs too.

Ever since this shop is open, i drop by almost every week w my colleagues and friends or sometimes alone, Sharon and team are wonderful, professional and friendly at the same time, their cakes sell like hot cakes, i mean cool cakes!!!! Not too sweet like Lady X, and just right w that later of sponge cake below and it taste like heaven w a cup of their specialty teas! Do drop by earlier of the day cos their cakes all sold out almost every day after 3pm!!! 🤣

The quality of the cake is great.
And the service is quite nice also, today is a little bit cold and the staff serves the cake with a cup of warm water. I appreciate it well.

Shaz Confections serves a refreshing variety of 16-layer crepe cakes that are fluffy, velvety and so beautiful that you can't resist taking a picture first before sinking your teeth into it. Best of all, it's not overly sweet.

Pandan Coconut Crepe Cake
-Creamy, Rich coconut and Pandan

Purple sweet potato and Matcha Crepe Cake
-Creamy, Rich, Matcha can be more rich 
-Purple Sweet potato: excellent, you can taste 
the grain of Purple Sweet potato 

Rose Lychee Crepe Cake
- A little bit Heavy, Just soso

I would prefer you guys to try the Purple sweet potato and Matcha Crepe Cake as the Purple Sweet potato flavoured one tastes really goooood!!!!!!

PS. ALL Sponge cakes: Moist, Soft, Smooth

reviews.text: 跌打後午餐😉

這間以千層蛋糕有名的小店位於西營盤，店內的環境很休閒，主打手工製的千層蛋糕，有很多不同的味道，有時還會有其他限定的味道。

今次試咗班蘭味， 一層層的感覺分明，忌廉打得十分幼滑，加多一杯咖啡就是一個令人精神的下午茶。

有名的手工千層蛋糕，有多種不同味道選擇
很好味
店舖不大
但很有休閒感覺，適直放空，談天
